{"id":2145,"date":"2024-11-22T16:17:03","date_gmt":"2024-11-22T16:17:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=2145"},"modified":"2024-12-01T03:12:39","modified_gmt":"2024-12-01T03:12:39","slug":"iv-changer","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/iv-changer\/","title":{"rendered":"IV Changer (NPC)"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left widesecond\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td><strong>Seaport City<\/strong> &#8211; Near the Seaport City Port by the water<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Purpose<\/th>\n<td>Maxes one or all IVs of a selected Pok\u00e9mon<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Transaction Item<\/th>\n<td>Bottle Caps\/Gold Bottle Caps<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cost<\/th>\n<td>\n        <strong>1 Stat\u2019s IV<\/strong> = 1 Bottle Cap<br \/>\n        <strong>All Stats IVs<\/strong> = 1 Gold Bottle Cap\n      <\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Start by flying to the Seaport City Pok\u00e9mon Center and going east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-seaport-city-pokemon-center-go-east.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Seaport City Pokemon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Seaport City Pokemon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Start going south after going down the set of stairs near the KBT Expressway entrance.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/02-pokemon-unbound-walking-south-after-going-down-the-stairs.jpg\" alt=\"Walking south after going down the stairs. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking south after going down the stairs.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The IV Changer is the purple-haired NPC at the end of the path, just outside the warehouse.<\/p>\n<div class=\"callout-box\"><strong>Note:<\/strong> If the NPC is not here at the correct time then you may need to adjust your difficulty to anything except vanilla.<\/div>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/03-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-iv-changer.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the IV Changer. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the IV Changer.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>Function<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/04-pokemon-unbound-the-services-offered-by-the-iv-changer.jpg\" alt=\"The services offered by the IV Changer. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The services offered by the IV Changer.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The IV Changer offers three primary services:<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>Increases one stat\u2019s IV on a selected Pokemon in exchange for <strong>one Bottle Cap<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Increases the IV of every stat on a selected Pokemon in exchange for <strong>one Gold Bottle Cap<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Viewing the EVs and IVs of every Pokemon in the player\u2019s party<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"299\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg 300w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Useful NPCs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":2146,"parent":2143,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[],"class_list":["post-2145","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/2145","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/2143"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2146"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2145"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2145"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}